Directed by Allison Craig. Shawn Seles. Drew Applegate.

Written by Claytia Gonsalves. Lucy Heavens. Kent Osborne. Quinn Elyse Scott. Nic Smal.

Cast Michael Croner (Barry Buns). Vella Lovell (Candle Fox). James Monroe Iglehart (Martin Chatterley). Deedee Magno (Miss Deer Teacher). Lucy Heavens (Additional Voices). Nic Smal (Principal Secretary). Eric Bauza (Reggie). Mary Mack (Additional Voices). Rachel House (Mary Buns). Lauren Ash (Beryl Chatterley). Nichole Sakura (Terri Buns). Brooke Dillman (Biker Lady). Josh Johnson (Harry Buns). Kent Osborne (Additional Voices). Eugene Cordero (Additional Voices). Rhys Darby (Trollie unknow). Gary Anthony Williams (Flam Bingo unknow). Tom Kenny (Darryn unknow). Kate Flannery (Agnes unknow). Steve Little (Glarbin Gloobin unknow). Katie Crown (Pawva unknow)

Language English.

Producers Winnie Chaffee. Kent Osborne.

Production Disney Channel. Disney Television Animation. Flixzilla Aura.

Creators Lucy Heavens. Nic Smal.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 6

Status On Going (2023)
